### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Configctl control-plane smoke tests
### ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@correlationId = test-http-configctl-001
@configId = d7a61c8eed779cc8d977cf108f1258df

### Create draft
POST {{baseUrl}}/configctl/configs
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "name": "payments-prod",
  "format": "json",
  "content": "{\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Payments Prod\",\"description\":\"baseline quality checks\"},\"bindings\":[{\"name\":\"payments\",\"topic\":\"billing.payment.created\"}],\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"payment_id\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true},{\"name\":\"status\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true}],\"rules\":[{\"name\":\"payment_id_required\",\"field\":\"payment_id\",\"operator\":\"required\",\"severity\":\"error\"},{\"name\":\"status_not_empty\",\"field\":\"status\",\"operator\":\"not_empty\",\"severity\":\"error\"}]}"
}

###

### Dry-run validate source content
POST {{baseUrl}}/configctl/configs/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "format": "json",
  "content": "{\"metadata\":{\"name\":\"Payments Prod\"},\"bindings\":[{\"name\":\"payments\",\"topic\":\"billing.payment.created\"}],\"fields\":[{\"name\":\"payment_id\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true}],\"rules\":[{\"name\":\"payment_id_required\",\"field\":\"payment_id\",\"operator\":\"required\",\"severity\":\"error\"}]}"
}

###

### Validate persisted draft
### Replace {{configId}} with the ID returned by create draft.
POST {{baseUrl}}/configctl/config-versions/{{configId}}/validate
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

###

### Compile validated version
POST {{baseUrl}}/configctl/config-versions/{{configId}}/compile
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{}

###

### Activate compiled version in the default global scope
POST {{baseUrl}}/configctl/config-versions/{{configId}}/activate
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

{
  "scope_kind": "global",
  "scope_key": "default"
}

###

### Get config version detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/configctl/config-versions/{{configId}}
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

###

### Get active config version detail for the default scope
GET {{baseUrl}}/configctl/active-config?scope_kind=global&scope_key=default
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}

###

### List config versions (summary shape)
GET {{baseUrl}}/configctl/config-versions
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-ID: {{correlationId}}
